  "libskTagline": "Shop Local. Dress Global.",
  "libskDescription": "LIBSK is Kuwait's fashion marketplace connecting shoppers with the best independent local boutiques, all in one place. Browse, order, and receive from your favourite Kuwait brands with ease.",
  "howCanWeHelpYouToday": "How can we help you today?",
