  "helpTopicBoutiques": "Boutiques",
  "helpOrdersQ1": "How do I track my order?",
  "helpOrdersA1": "Once your order is placed, you can track it from the Orders section in your profile. You will see real-time status updates as your order is processed and delivered.",
  "helpOrdersQ2": "Can I cancel my order?",
  "helpOrdersA2": "Orders can be cancelled within 1 hour of placement. After that, the boutique may have already begun processing it. Contact us immediately if you need to cancel.",
  "helpOrdersQ3": "My order shows delivered but I have not received it.",
  "helpOrdersA3": "Please check with neighbours or building reception first. If the item is still missing, contact our support team within 48 hours and we will investigate.",
  "helpOrdersQ4": "How do I open a dispute?",
  "helpOrdersA4": "You have 7 days from the delivery date to open a dispute. Go to your Orders, select the relevant order, and tap Open Dispute. Describe your issue and submit. Please note that boutique owners and admins have the right to review and reject disputes based on the nature and validity of the claim.",
  "helpDeliveryQ1": "What areas do you deliver to?",
  "helpDeliveryA1": "We currently deliver across all governorates in Kuwait including Capital, Hawalli, Farwaniya, Ahmadi, Jahra, and Mubarak Al-Kabeer.",
  "helpDeliveryQ2": "How long does delivery take?",
  "helpDeliveryA2": "Delivery times depend on the delivery type you select and your location. Standard delivery typically takes 2 to 4 business days. Same-day delivery is available for select areas.",
  "helpDeliveryQ3": "How much does delivery cost?",
  "helpDeliveryA3": "Delivery fees depend on the type of delivery selected and the delivery area. The exact fee will be shown at checkout before you confirm your order.",
  "helpReturnsQ1": "What is the return policy?",
  "helpReturnsA1": "LIBSK has a 7-day return window from the date of delivery. Return eligibility may also depend on the individual boutique requirements. Please check the boutique storefront for any additional conditions before purchasing.",
  "helpReturnsQ2": "How do I return an item?",
  "helpReturnsA2": "To initiate a return, go to your Orders, select the item, and tap Request Return. Our team will coordinate with the boutique on your behalf.",
  "helpReturnsQ3": "How long do refunds take?",
  "helpReturnsA3": "Once a return is approved, refunds are processed within 5 to 7 business days depending on your payment method.",
  "helpPaymentQ1": "What payment methods are accepted?",
  "helpPaymentA1": "We accept KNet, Visa, Mastercard, Apple Pay, debit cards, credit cards, and Deema.",
  "helpPaymentQ2": "Is my payment information secure?",
  "helpPaymentA2": "Yes. We do not store any card details. All transactions are processed through secure, encrypted payment gateways.",
  "helpPaymentQ3": "I was charged but my order was not placed.",
  "helpPaymentA3": "This can happen due to a connection issue. Please contact us immediately with your payment reference and we will resolve it within 24 hours.",
  "helpAccountQ1": "How do I change my password?",
  "helpAccountA1": "Go to Profile, tap Your Account, then tap Change Password. You will receive a reset link to your registered email.",
  "helpAccountQ2": "How do I update my delivery address?",
  "helpAccountA2": "Go to Profile, then Saved Addresses. You can add, edit, or remove addresses at any time.",
  "helpAccountQ3": "How do I delete my account?",
  "helpAccountA3": "You can delete your account from the Profile page under Your Account settings. Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone.",
  "helpBoutiquesQ1": "How do I become a boutique owner on LIBSK?",
  "helpBoutiquesA1": "Send us an email at boutiques@libsk.com with details about your boutique. Our team will review your application and get back to you within 3 business days.",
  "helpBoutiquesQ2": "Can I save a boutique to view later?",
  "helpBoutiquesA2": "Yes. Tap the save icon on any boutique storefront to add it to your Saved Boutiques in your profile.",
  "helpBoutiquesQ3": "A boutique is not responding to my order.",
  "helpBoutiquesA3": "If a boutique has not updated your order status within 48 hours, contact our support team and we will follow up on your behalf.",
